Ukasha Salihu, popularly known as DJ Amson, has won the Best Music Distribution Award at the Northern Pandora Awards 2022. He was the first young successful Youtuber, Music Distributor, Talent Manager, and also Social Media Influencer from Northern Nigeria to win the award. DJ Amson was born in Kebbi State but is currently resident in Kano State. Being the first youngest music distributor in the North, DJ Amson is opportuned to work with different artistes of different Industries around the globe. Apart from the music distribution, Dj Amson is also a social media influencer as he handles all kinds of social media. Furthermore, Dj Amson is a great YouTuber having big numbers, he sells and buy YouTube channels and also grow YouTube channel for his clients. On what the award means to him, he said, “It means a breakthrough and a milestone to me as I pursue my career. I believe the publication will increase the visibility of my services.” On his next target, he said: “To increase my clientele base, improve my services to win more awards.”